abstract: >
  Career-Ops RU is a fork of career-ops by Santiago Fernández de Valderrama,
  adapted for the Russian-speaking job market. Adds hh.ru, Habr Career and
  getmatch.ru integrations, Russian-language prompts, RU salary scoring,
  and n8n automation pipeline for Telegram notifications.

